# Registro usuario cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Usuario",
  "apellido": "Prueba",
  "email": "cliente@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "rol": "client"
}

